data.description: Welcome home!  This 2 story townhome offers an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bath, fireplace and eat in kitchen.  Upstairs laundry is super convenient to bedrooms.  The oven/stove and microwave were replaced in 2023 and the water heater was replaced in 2022.  Recent flooring downstairs as well as new carpet upstairs!  There is an outdoor back patio for grilling and your own private storage area.  Your amenities in Regent Park include pool, tennis courts, playground and walking trails.  Located minutes from Carowinds Theme Park, restaurants, shopping and easy I-77 access.
